comment._content:
This is not USCG V218, N744, it an ex US Navy J4F-2 BuAer 37730 C/N 1360. 
V218 C/N 1266 would have had a topside hatch, this Widgeon doesn't have one.
There were 2 Widgeons registered N744, this is the second one, it is still flying and working for a living in Alaska as N17481.
